Indian Oil Issues First Tender to Buy Crude for August Loading

-- B y   S h e r r y   S u
-- 
2011-06-07T10:29:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-07/indian-oil-issues-first-tender-to-buy-crude-for-august-loading.html
Indian Oil Corp., the country’s
biggest refiner, issued its first spot tender for crude for
loading in August, official documents obtained by Bloomberg News
show. The company bought seven cargoes totaling about 6.6
million barrels of West African grades for loading in July.  Details of the company’s requirements are as follows:  To contact the reporter on this story:
